idānīṃidānī rājayogāc charīrerājayogāc charīre ||rājayogācharīrerājayogāśarīrerogayogācharīre etādṛśāniyādṛśāni cihnāni bhavanti/ tāni kathyante/ cf. YSv (PT p. 844): yasya darśanamātreṇa rogaśokavivarjitaḥ | paramānandacittaḥ syāt tapasvī caiva kīrttitaḥ | saptadvīpā bhaved dṛṣṭā tattvajñānaṃ tato bhavet | sarvabhāvaṃ vijānīyād vajradeho bhavet tathā | sarpadaṣṭe viṣaṃ na syāt kṣudhā nidrā tṛṣā tathā |sakalaroganāśaḥsakalarogaḥ nāśaḥ/ sakala:pṛthvīṃsakalāṃ pṛthvīṃ paśyati/ tad anantaraṃtad aṃtaraṃtad anaṃtara° tattvaviṣayaṃom. jñānam utpadyate/ samagrāṃ bhāṣāṃsamagrā bhāṣāsamagrā bhāṣasamagra bhāṣā jānāti/ tataḥ puruṣasya deho vajramayo bhavati/ sarpadaṃśe°daṃśo°daṃśena°daṃśema satisatīom. maraṇaṃ naom. bhavatibhavatīvati/ tataḥtat°om. puruṣasyaom. bubhukṣābunnukṣābabhukṣāom.pipāsanidroṣṇatāpipāsanidroṣṭṇatā°pipāsanidrā | uṣṇatā ||pipāsanidrollatāpipāsanidrolmatāom.śītaśītatāśītoṣṇatāśīta nāom.bādhāṃ na kurvantikurotiom./
